Package: eBacktestCraft
Title: Professional Backtesting Framework for Quantitative Strategies
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Yishuo", family = "Deng", email = "dengyishuo@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person(given = "Yishuo", family = "Deng", role = "ctb", comment = "eFactorCraft author")
  )
Description: A comprehensive backtesting framework designed to work seamlessly 
    with eFactorCraft. Supports multiple rebalance modes (calendar/threshold),
    advanced stop-loss mechanisms (fixed/trailing/hybird), portfolio constraints,
    transaction costs, and comprehensive performance analytics. Includes professional
    visualization tools for equity curves, drawdowns, and return distributions.
    Perfect for quantitative strategy research and factor-based investing.
